***************************
Scala in practice exercises
***************************

First part : slideshare presentation

Second part : exercices
   - all you need is a play framework in your path, mysql with world database (db folder in play-scala)
   - just run some play idealize / eclipsify on projects (idea and javascript projects in idea and play-scala in eclipse)
   - open REPL and play with List, Map, Function, Option...
   - open idea project and answer questions
   - open javascript project, start play and play with functionaljavascript, underscore and custom javascript functions maybe and either
   - open play scrapbook (in scala module) and play with it
   - finally, open play-scala, start play and add some actions (exercices) and finish with some sql queries using Anorm

All solutions are in {project}-solution projects.

Enjoy ^^
